需求:根据编号查询员工信息及所在的部门信息 

实体类添加一个部门作为属性 




实体类 




1.  @AllArgsConstructor
2.  @NoArgsConstructor
3.  @Data
4.  public class Emp implements Serializable {
5.      private Integer empno;
6.      private String ename;
7.      private String job;
8.      private Integer mgr;
9.      private Date hiredate;
10.     private Double sal;
11.     private Double comm;
12.     private Integer deptno;
13.     // 组合一个Dept对象作为自己的属性
14.     private Dept dept;
15. }

 

接口 










1.  public interface EmpMapper {
2.      /**
3.       * 根据员工编号查询员工的所有信息并携带所在的部门信息
4.       * @param empno 要查询的员工编号
5.       * @return Emp对象,组合了Dept对象作为属性,对部门信息进行存储
6.       */
7.      Emp findEmpJoinDeptByEmpno(int empno);
8.  }

 




映射文件 










1.  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
2.  <!DOCTYPE mapper
3.          PUBLIC "-//mybatis.org//DTD Mapper 3.0//EN"
4.          "http://mybatis.org/dtd/mybatis-3-mapper.dtd">
5.  <mapper namespace="com.msb.mapper.EmpMapper">
6.      <!--Emp findEmpJoinDeptByEmpno(int empno);-->
7.      <resultMap id="empJoinDept" type="emp">
8.          <!--设置emp本身的八个属性的映射关系-->
9.          <id property="empno" column="empno"></id>
10.         <result property="ename" column="ename"></result>
11.         <result property="job" column="job"></result>
12.         <result property="sal" column="sal"></result>
13.         <result property="hiredate" column="hiredate"></result>
14.         <result property="mgr" column="mgr"></result>
15.         <result property="comm" column="comm"></result>
16.         <result property="deptno" column="deptno"></result>
17.         <!--
18.         association 处理一对一
19.         封装一对一信息关系的标签
20.         property  emp类的属性名
21.         javaType  用哪个类的对象给属性赋值
22.         -->
23.         <association property="dept" javaType="dept">
24.             <id column="deptno" property="deptno"></id>
25.             <result column="dname" property="dname"></result>
26.             <result column="loc" property="loc"></result>
27.         </association>
28.     </resultMap>
29.     <select id="findEmpJoinDeptByEmpno" resultMap="empJoinDept" >
30.         select * from
31.         emp e
32.         left join dept  d
33.         on e.deptno =d.deptno
34.         where empno = #{empno}
35.     </select>
36. </mapper>
